{
  "stem": "27390.4",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So my mother and my sister went along, and they saw this man, Chaim Rumkowski.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there were a lot-- already a lot of women in the same position as my mother.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They had lost their husbands.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Well, we didn't know yet whether they'd been shot.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We were hoping that they were just frightening these people to get money out of them, valuables.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And this Rumkowski, he, himself, didn't know what happened.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He's said, I'll try and find out what happened to these men.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And if they had been shot, at least I'll try.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They should be-- the bodies should be brought back to the ghetto and be buried in a Jewish burial.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "That he could never find out.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He made inquiries.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "The police, the Lodz police, the German police, told him that this was a special action carried out by the SS.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And it was not under the jurisdiction of the local police.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But we know, from that, two people that were also shot managed to get away from the pits where they buried these bodies.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They were injured.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And they-- they somehow managed to-- they hid.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "They stayed there till everything quieted down in that place.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And they came back into the ghetto a few days later.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And they told the story of what happened to these men.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "These men were taken.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "They were shot.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And they were taken on lorries and taken out-- outside the city, somewhere in a field.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And pits were already dug there, ready for them.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And they were thrown off the lorries into the pits.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And soldiers went around with bayonets, with the bayonets in their rifles.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And whoever was still alive was killed off, with a bayonet, to make sure that they're dead.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "But somehow, these two men managed to get away.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
